Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomari: So, let's see what you can spin this year
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.99,0:00:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakusa: When the waxing moon has waned twice more
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.49,0:00:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakusa: Comes 'the day' you'd spun my wheels before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakusa: And so I ask of the Rose Witch tonight\NTell this servant...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji: Isn't there anything fun to do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.52,0:00:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like? 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,P-p-p-p-p-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's CardFight Pro-Wrestling!!\NP-p-p-p-p-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's CardFight Pro-Wrestling!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Pro-wrestling?!\NThat's CardFight Pro-Wrestling!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pro-wrestling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of retiring as a Cardfighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you say you're gonna be a pro wrestler?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, not so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, something's the matter with you lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.39,0:02:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Something being the matter is \Nvery much his usual mode of operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:02:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So again, why pro-wrestling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asked to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pro-Wrestling Association \N Assembly Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,By the old man from the\N Neighborhood Pro-Wrestling Association.\NPro-Wrestling Association \N Assembly Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pro-Wrestling Association \N Assembly Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,professional wrestling is currently \Non the verge of extinction in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a man to inherit this mask \Nand resurrect the Pro-Wrestling Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have long searched for such a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You will help me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji the man will be a pro-wrestler!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And well, that's the story in a nutshell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, second?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And you should have second thoughts about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, that's why I need to \Nbuild up my body by next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That filled me up good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... but wondering \Nif we can really win this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever comes, I won't run or hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll defeat 'em fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear it on my big thumb here! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:04:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Neighborhood Pro-Wrestling Association \Ncouldn't bring in that big a deal of a wrestler!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Zakusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A signing ceremony? It's like a title match. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this kinda large-scale?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Danji Momoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I am, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Enthusiastic about this match?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? W-Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna beat him to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who's coming, \Nbut now's his brief chance to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are some calling this \Nan ill-advised challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a town revitalization event...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you accept a challenge from an unknown?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us about your enthusiasm for this match!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us a statement please, Mr. Tanahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What the? It's Zakusa, \Nand... Hiroshi Tanahashi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, step down! \NI won't make fun of you, so just quit, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Zakusa, what's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's no third-string, \Nhe's a super big-league wrestler!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Zakusa! Just what are you pulling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I could've sworn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I take a Skyrocketing Elbow, \Nor something like that?! Tell me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Exciting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You there, do you play cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You a strong player?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji's the strongest Cardfighter around! \NHe's called the Tiger of Kaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Danji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi Tanahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What superhuman strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're last-week's and last-last-week's issues, \Nso I had no problem with tearing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight... Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could lend me an ear, Mr. Tanahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna beat you senseless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Zakusa, what did you tell him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided how the two of us will fight:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,CardFight Pro-Wrestling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,CardFight Pro-Wrestling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Cards are another strong point of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How 'bout you and me duke it out in both arenas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro's gonna Cardfight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent! Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they trade their written oaths, \Nthese two will be mutual enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the moment when this \Nunprecedented title match becomes reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No regrets, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder Hill: Land of Dreams\NWhy didn't you call me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I never heard that Tanahashi was coming!\NWonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, neither did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Blasted Zakusa, pitting me against Tanahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite his usual manner, \NZakky can be unexpectedly dynamic at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But you looked really cool there, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying, "Fight me!" to THE Hiroshi Tanahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's this "CardFight Pro-Wrestling" thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you do a round of Cardfighting, \Nthen a round of pro-wrestling, and repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like Chess Boxing, where you \Nalternate between chess and boxing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! That's just your kinda fight, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you perhaps having regrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I have any?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, this is a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And going up against someone \Noverwhelmingly strong is what makes fights fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, this is Tanahashi here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to stay calm, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I go about fighting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you win the Cardfighting in the first round,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,then you won't have to do any wrestling, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Great idea, Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I worried for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, that's no fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'd rather see me get killed by Tanahashi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget I asked!\NWonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Bro! You can beat him in Round 1!\NWonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it'll be an easy win!\NWonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it'll be an easy win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,CardFight Pro-Wrestling Deathmatch - 12 Rounds \N Tanahashi vs Momoyama
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,CardFight Pro-Wrestling Deathmatch - 12 Rounds
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right before the match, \Nyou don't need to eat it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, is your deck--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'm all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, I'm the Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause you didn't chew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go buy some more water bottles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Cigarettes/Alcohol          Coffee 100 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm his second!\NCigarettes/Alcohol          Coffee 100 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Cigarettes/Alcohol          Coffee 100 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this be enough water?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this more than enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The young lady seems to be \Ngreatly enjoying herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Zakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Town residents!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to start the insane deathmatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting to see Tanahashi \Nup this close... it's making me giddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops! Gotta do my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In the blue corner, \Nthe nightmare born of Kaga:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji Mo-- huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,With the essence inherited from \NKaga's delicate specialty, Kobako snow crab, 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow-Crab Mask is on the scene! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow-Crab Mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This mask was entrusted to me \Nby the head of the Pro-Wrestling Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on your side, Snow-Crab Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In the red corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Once-in-a-Century Talent descends to Kaga! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi Tanahashi enters the arena!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Tanahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Both players are presented with bouquets!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm his second...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakusa told us there's a labor shortage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl in the green dress is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that girl's my type by a long shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow! It's sliding! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's break it up, now...\NOw ow ow! It's sliding! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Round 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanguard!\NStand up, Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Once in a Century Talent \NHiroshi Tanahashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,versus local hero Snow-Crab Mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in the first ever CardFight \NPro-Wrestling Deathmatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The first round is a Cardfight round!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Snow-Crab Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight hard, Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh! Snow-Crab Mask is making his move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let it get to a pro-wrestling round!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's end this before it starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! ...I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanahashi's just that brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The round's gonna end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, to think I'd get to \NCardfight against Tanahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take a moment, \Nand unleash the coolest move, ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot! I got too into it and lost track!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Round 2: Pro-Wrestling
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Plan A, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The second round is pro-wrestling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The arena where Tanahashi is unrivaled!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh, Tanahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Slipping out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a crab! I'm a crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow-Crab Mask makes a crab-run \Nto escape beneath the ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:16:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow-Crab Mask's back out! \NTanahashi's after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tanahashi's Dragon Screw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I give, I give!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Plan A failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No other choice, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh! Now there's more Snow-Crab Masks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really tough! \NWhich one of them is the real one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He figured it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Another game of tag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back in the ring and fight, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji! Here's some water!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget water! I can't even see the cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta survive, Snow-Crab Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can keep going!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm gonna do this... pro-wrestling!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the Vanguard part?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The sight of him getting more and more cornered,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is frankly my favorite treat! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit him harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu! Throw in the towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't he throwing it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"What's wrong, tired already?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanahashi's suddenly heated up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oraa!! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessssss!\NNooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Orrraa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A Sling Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tanahashi at his finest! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can he no longer stand up?! No, Snow-Crab Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In the face of the Once in a Century Talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is this the farthest you can get \Nwith the power of crab essence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"Now take this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow-Crab Mask does a Cross Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,His crab pincers strike at Tanahashi's throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither budges an inch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a flesh against flesh, bone against bone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,will against will collision!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A Twelve Six! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dropped down headfirst! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Who could've foreseen this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the stance for Tanahashi's \Ngreatest finishing move, High Fly Flow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You did brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow-Crab Mask can do nothing more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lookit that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredibly, Snow-Crab Mask \Nhas interrupted the High Fly Flow finish! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow Crab! Snow Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow Crab! Snow Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow Crab! Snow Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!\NSnow Crab! Snow Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanahashi gets the three count!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Knew you'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,People of Kaga, I love you! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji! Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost, big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I looked uncool in front of you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't uncool at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, you risked your life to advertise \Nthe Neighborhood Pro-Wrestling Association!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.81,0:22:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now some life has been breathed \Ninto this town's pro-wrestling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.19,0:22:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The CardFight Pro-Wrestling Association \Nthat you built with your family is alive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with your future endeavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I never built such an association.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,0:22:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This town has no pro-wrestling association.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.79,0:22:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No Neighborhood Pro-Wrestling Association?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.15,0:22:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No Card Pro-Wrestling Association?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither exist. It was all made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.39,0:22:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Made up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why did you have me--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tanahashi! You were incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakusa! Once in a while, you're pretty capable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the best ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.88,0:22:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I set up this fight for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:22:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...today is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.89,0:23:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...our anniversary, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.54,0:23:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what anni--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.27,0:23:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to give you a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.15,0:23:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.39,0:23:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You must want a reward if you went this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.99,0:23:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be giving you your reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In spades.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My, something like that could be nice, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... wh-wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want anything like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.61,0:23:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now suffer for every injury I took!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Quit dodging!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So close!\NI missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.84,0:23:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How about here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.48,0:23:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!\NHow about here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.31,0:25:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Check Out My Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.99,0:25:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tohya.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.88,0:25:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.35,0:26:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now to make the most of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.11,0:26:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's when I introduce my Apex Ruler, Bastion!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.20,0:26:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Using its continuous ability, Bastion gives \Nall your grade 3 units +2000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.19,0:26:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you went first against \Nan opponent's grade 2 of 10,000 power,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.36,0:26:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the +2000 power would let a grade 3 \Nattack it with 15,000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.27,0:26:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The bonus means that your single unit's attack \Nhas a guard requirement of 10,000! 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.95,0:26:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if you went second, a boost of 8000 \Nwould give your column 23,000 power,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.91,0:26:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so against an opponent's grade 3 of 13,000-- 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.94,0:26:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.20,0:26:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Episode 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.21,0:26:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder Child 
